Notes:

1) if mod1.sh is created or modified on a Windows machine, you will get an error. In the terminal on the cluster, run:
dos2unix mod1.sh

2) To install INLA on the HPC:
> install.packages("INLA",repos=c(getOption("repos"),INLA="https://inla.r-inla-download.org/R/testing"), dep=TRUE)

>library(INLA)

> options(timeout=300)

> inla.binary.install()

>library (INLA)
